      "SEO stands for search engine optimization. Google and Bing help potential customers find products and services that match their interests. They have algorithms that efficiently analyze numerous sites and determine their ranking for any specific keyword. Now, you may have the most beautiful site, but if you may have the opportunity to grow your business further by improving your ranking in the search engines.",
