      "Below, we list 5 best small business SEO strategies that will help boost business growth. While it is possible to spend a lot of time getting the ideal ranking of search engines over time, investing an hour a day in SEO or hiring a qualified digital marketing agency like Prime Marketing Experts can begin to attract more traffic.",
      "If you have ever searched for a business in Google or Bing, you will notice that the platform often recognizes where we are geographically searching.",
      "Here are three easy ways to tell search engines where your business is located and which areas do you serve:",
